Reflex.SayString: Ah, <cycle> Cycle! <Kodu> Kodu has brought you home safely! <Kodu> Kodu, a terrible sickness has befallen our magic flying <turtle> turtles! It is said that only a Golden <apple> Apple will cure them! Will you help us by finding the Golden <apple>Apple? Legend says the <apple> can be found beyond the valley.

Hi, <kodu> Kodu! My father asked me to come find you! Something is happening back at the farm! Can you help us? With your perfect hearing, if you listen for our <hut>hut, you should be able to get there. I will follow you.
<coin> Coin, please! Anyone wishing to pass must pay one <coin> coin!
Thank you! You may pass. But before you do, beware! You are passing into the Cursed Lands! Remember to stay on the "Invisible Path"!

Hello, <Kodu> brave traveler! The only thing these evil <Saucer> Saucers like to eat more than <Kodu> brave travelers is green <apple> Apples. I saved this one last <apple> apple for a good person like you. When the time is right, I hope it will help you!

With this <coin>coin, I can cross the bridge! But that bridge is very narrow... Will you help me to cross safely by programming me to move according to your directions? Program me to move using the <gamepad>gamepad left stick, by using the <keyboard>keyboard keys up, left & right, or by using the <leftmouse>mouse left click. (Press [Esc] or <back> to start editing.)
Ah, the Golden <apple> Apple! If I can get it, I can save my friend <Cycle> Cycle's farm!! How can I distract those evil <Saucer> Saucers???
